TY  - JOUR
TI  - An Application of Least Squares to Family Diet Surveys
AU  - Quenouille, M. H.
AB  - [The application of the method of least squares is discussed for the case in which a large number of unknowns have to be estimated; in particular, the application to family diet surveys is considered. Methods are indicated for shortening the analysis and investigating the importance of different variables by a step-by-step procedure. Suggestions are made on the planning of surveys in the light of the methods investigated here.]
